{
  "stem": "11998.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, actually, my friends were some of the Jewish people that I knew from school.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were my closest friends.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But because they lived further away, my everyday friends were the people who were my neighbors right in the-- on the block.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were Christians, Catholics most of them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we used to get along very well, except for Easter, when they came from the church, and the priests used to say, you know, the Jews are the Christ killers.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so, for about two weeks I had to hide from them, and we didn't play together because they used to call me Christ killer.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And as far as that goes, every-- every courtyard had their own gang.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was part of our courtyard's gang.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we had wars between our courtyard and the next door courtyard.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And-- but that was the way-- the way it went.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Gangs of kids, one against the other.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was accepted among my friends in my block, except at Easter.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And even then, it was sort of watered down as to what happened if they caught me outside of my yard.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that they're going to school, we used to go in groups of students.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because otherwise, if I was caught by myself, there would be-- there would be enough gangs in the city that, if I wasn't caught by one, I would be caught by others.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my technique was to go against the wall and look up at the building opposite and say-- and start yelling, Ma or Dad, So that they thought that I lived there and that I was going to get help.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Even so, it was blocks away from my home.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
